
       libcam1394,  1394-based digital camera controll library.

       http://www.ccm.media.kyoto-u.ac.jp/~yoshimoto/libcam1394
        
FEATURES
--------

* general
   - support for 1394-based digital camera specifaction 1.4
   - multiple cameras support
   - multiple OHCI 1394 I/F boards support

* color conversation
   - support for IPL (Intel's image processing library) image
   structure

* CUI 
   - try "cam1394 --help" for details

and there are some sample codes in the sample/ directory.


